OL,6,FMore than 27,000 healthcare workers
OL,7,Fare set to receive two one-off
OL,8,Fpayments worth up to #3,000, the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,10,F(DHSC) has said.
OL,12,FThe payments ` worth at least #1,665 `
OL,13,Fwill benefit community nurses, sexual
OL,14,Fhealth workers, speech-and-language
OL,15,Ftherapists, physiotherapists, and
OL,16,Fother frontline workers at non-NHS
OL,17,Forganisations.
