OL,6,FThe DHSC said the payments will
OL,7,Frecognise the vital role of healthcare
OL,8,Fworkers at social enterprises,
OL,9,Fcharities, private providers and local
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FLast year, more than one million NHS
OL,13,Fstaff received two one-off payments
OL,14,Falongside a 5% pay rise.
OL,16,FHowever, these payments only applied
OL,17,Fto those directly employed by NHS
OL,18,Forganisations.
