OL,6,FForming part of the wider NHS pay
OL,7,Fdeal, the DHSC said that one of the
OL,8,Fnew payments was specifically intended
OL,9,Fto recognise the efforts healthcare
OL,10,Fworkers had made to cut waiting lists.
OL,12,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,13,FVictoria Atkins said: "I hugely value
OL,14,Fthe hard work of all our healthcare
OL,15,Fstaff, and those working in non-NHS
OL,16,Forganisations offer vital support to
OL,17,Fpatients.
